<MELItem itemNbr="21-27-26" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-21-27-26.1.2-21-27-26">
<Title>Aft EE Cooling Supply Fan</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="2" nbrRequired="1" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>One may be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Inoperative aft equipment cooling supply fan is deactivated.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Flight is conducted pressurized.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Deactivate the inoperative aft equipment cooling supply fan (AMM DDG 21-27-26).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>For fan 1 inoperative:</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the following circuit breakers and lock with an INOP tag:</Para>
<List listType="1)">
<ListItem>
<Para>MC-SUPPLY FAN 1 	AFT EQUIP CLG</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>EQUIP CLG SUPPLY FAN-AFT 1</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>For fan 2 inoperative:</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the following circuit breakers and lock with an INOP tag:</Para>
<List listType="1)">
<ListItem>
<Para>MC-SUPPLY FAN 2 	AFT EQUIP CLG</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>EQUIP CLG SUPPLY FAN-AFT 2</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
